name: Magical Cherry Blossoms (cropped)
description:
Title: Magical Cherry Blossoms (cropped)
Location: Salem, Oregon
Year Taken: 2020
About this photo:  One of the places I photographed during the early days of the COVID-19 pandemic was the Oregon State Capitol. The grounds feature a deep mall lined with cherry blossom trees and two sidewalks on each side leading to the capitol building itself. As I was trying to capture the falling leaves, I set up pointing down one of the sidewalks and kept the photograph. It was just OK, not a particularly compelling shot. Then one day, months later, I opened my files again and saw something hiding inside the original photograph. I saw a piece of artwork. This is the result.
